'''安大略402號省道'''（{{lang-en|Ontario Highway 402}}），正式名稱為'''國王402號公路'''（{{lang|en|King's Highway 402}}），是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]]一條東西向[[400系列公路|400系列]][[高速公路|高速公路]]，連接位於該省[[南安大略|西南部]]的[[倫敦_(加拿大)|倫敦]]和[[薩尼亞|薩尼亞]]，並在其西端駁上[[藍水大橋|藍水大橋]]跨越[[美加邊境|美加邊境]]通往[[美國|美國]][[密芝根州|密芝根州]]曉倫港，構成來往安省和[[美國中西部|美國中西部]]的其中一條主要貿易走廊。

== 走線 ==
[[File:Highway_401-Highway_402_interchange.jpg|thumb]]
402號公路西起[[藍水大橋|藍水大橋]]位於愛德華角（{{lang|en|Point Edward}}）的落腳點<ref>{{cite web
 | title      = Tourist Information Map
 | publisher      = Visit Point Edward
 | url      = http://www.visitpointedward.com/map.html
 | accessdate      = February 21, 2011
 | archive-date      = 2016-03-04
 | archive-url      = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304035935/http://www.visitpointedward.com/map.html
 | dead-url      = no
 }}</ref>，途經加拿大的邊檢關卡後進入薩尼亞市，與40號公路交匯後從南面掠過薩尼亞克里斯·哈德菲爾德機場（{{lang|en|Sarnia Chris Hadfield Airport}}），直達薩尼亞市的東界<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Directions
 |publisher   = Sarnia Chris Hadfield Airport
 |url         = http://www.sarniaairport.com/directions.php
 |accessdate  = February 21, 2011
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20110430090441/http://www.sarniaairport.com/directions.php
 |archivedate = 2011年4月30日
}}</ref>。此後402號公路隨著沿線農地的南北分界線往東伸延，其走線因此非常筆直<ref>{{Google maps

 | title      = Satellite view of Highway 402 east of Sarnia; note its position midway between London Line and Michigan Line
 | url        = http://maps.google.ca/?ie=UTF8&ll=42.991967,-82.25481&spn=0.057633,0.154324&t=h&z=13
 | accessdate = February 21, 2011}}</ref>，到斯特拉斯羅伊（{{lang|en|Strathroy}}）以北才改為東南－西北走向，在德拉瓦鎮（{{lang|en|Delaware}}）以南往東伸延，進入[[倫敦_(加拿大)|倫敦市]]後與4號公路和溫德蘭道（{{lang|en|Wonderland Road}}）交匯，再往東伸延至[[安大略401號省道|401號公路]]為止。此交匯處只設順方向行車線之間的匝道（即402號公路東行線往401號公路東行線，和401號公路西行線往402號公路西行線），來往反方向行車線之間的車流需途經4號公路<ref name="2010 mapart">{{cite map

 | title       = Ontario Back Road Atlas
 | year        = 2010
 | publisher   = Peter Heiler
 | cartography = [[MapArt|MapArt]]
 | pages       = 12–15
 | section     = T7–U17
 | isbn        = 978-1-55198-226-7}}</ref>。

==歷史==
[[File:Highway_402_approaching_Blue_Water_Bridge,_June_2013.jpg|thumb]]
連接薩尼亞和美國[[密芝根州|密芝根州]]曉倫港的[[藍水大橋|藍水大橋]]於1938年10月10日通車<ref>{{cite web
 |title        = Construction of the Original Span
 |publisher    = Blue Water Bridge Canada
 |date         = February 22, 2008
 |url          = http://www.bwba.org/original_e.html
 |accessdate   = February 21, 2011
 |quote        = After dedication ceremonies on October 7th, 8th, and 9th, the Bridge was opened for regular traffic on October 10, 1938.
 |archive-date = 2017-09-02
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20170902173810/http://www.bwba.org/original_e.html
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>，而安大略省政府則從同年起在大橋的加拿大端落腳點興建一條長{{convert|6.1|km|mi}}的雙程分隔道路。此道路名為藍水大橋連接路（{{lang|en|Blue Water Bridge Approach}}），於1940年代末開通，並於三處設有平交路口<ref>{{cite map

 | title       = Ontario Road Map
 | cartography = C.P. Robins
 | publisher   = Ontario Department of Highways
 | year        = 1946
 | inset       = Sarnia}}</ref><ref>{{cite map

 | title       = Ontario Road Map
 | cartography = C.P. Robins
 | publisher   = Ontario Department of Highways
 | year        = 1949
 | inset       = Sarnia}}</ref>，東端與40號公路較接。此道路於1952年獲編為402號公路，與400號和401號公路一起成為安大略省首批400系列公路。

省政府於1957年末正式宣佈將402號公路往東伸延至401號公路<ref>{{cite news
 | title       = Sarnia Link to 401 in Project
 | work       = The Windsor Daily Star
 | date       = September 12, 1957
 | page       = 20
 | url       = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=pCU_AAAAIBAJ&sjid=FFAMAAAAIBAJ&dq=superhighway%20ontario&pg=1689%2C2153993
 | accessdate       = December 15, 2011
 | archive-date       = 2022-03-17
 | archive-url       = https://web.archive.org/web/20220317194709/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=pCU_AAAAIBAJ&sjid=FFAMAAAAIBAJ&dq=superhighway%20ontario&pg=1689%2C2153993
 }}</ref>，而具體走線則於1968年2月公佈<ref>{{cite book
 |title        = Annual Report
 |publisher    = Ontario Department of Highways
 |year         = 1967
 |page         = 76
 |section      = Construction
 |url          = http://books.google.com/books?id=LyZvE2PAjpwC&q=%22highway+402%22+Sarnia&dq=%22highway+402%22+Sarnia&hl=en&ei=S_0iTMebCcL7lwe2uvXpDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAQ
 |accessdate   = February 21, 2011
 |quote        = Several important freeway projects were completed including the 98-km Highway 402, Sarnia to London
 |archive-date = 2014-05-07
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20140507075558/http://books.google.com/books?id=LyZvE2PAjpwC&q=%22highway+402%22+Sarnia&dq=%22highway+402%22+Sarnia&hl=en&ei=S_0iTMebCcL7lwe2uvXpDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAQ
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>。40號公路以東的工程於1972年展開<ref>{{cite book

 | title     = Highway Construction Program: King's and Secondary Highways
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1972–1973
 | page      = xi}}</ref>，而介乎40號和21號公路的路段則於1978年10月13日通車<ref>{{cite press release

 | title     = Phase Two of Highway 402 Officially Opened October 13
 | author    = Public and Safety Information Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | date      = October 13, 1978}}</ref>。介乎21號和81號公路、以及介乎2號和401號公路的路段於1978年末動工<ref>{{cite map

 | title       = Ontario Road Map
 | cartography = Cartography Section
 | publisher   = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year        = 1978/79
 | section     = L18–M20}}</ref>；前者於1979年11月26日開通<ref>{{cite press release

 | title     = Official Opening of Highway 402 (Phase III) Warwick to Highway 81
 | author    = Public and Safety Information Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | date      = November 26, 1979}}</ref>，後者則於1981年11月17日開通<ref>{{cite news

 | title      = New Section Opens on Highway to U.S.
 | work       = The Toronto Star
 | date       = November 18, 1981
 | page       = A25}}</ref>。

2號和81號公路之間的路段於1982年末完成，而402號公路西端位於河岸街（{{lang|en|Front Street}}）的平交路口亦於同期改建成立交橋，402號公路遂於1982年11月10日正式全線啓用<ref>{{cite book

 | title      = Annual Report
 | url      = https://archive.org/details/annualreportd1978mass
 | publisher  = Ontario Department of Highways
 | year       = 1982–1983
 | page       = [https://archive.org/details/annualreportd1978mass/page/76 76]
 | section    = Construction}}</ref>。

2010年12月13日，安省西南部受[[大湖效應|大湖效應]]所造成的雪颮吹襲，大雪導致402號公路約{{convert|80|km|mi}}的路段關閉數天。[[蘭布頓縣|蘭布頓縣]]政府宣佈進入緊急狀態，而時任聯邦國防部長[[彼得·麥凱|彼得·麥凱]]則調派兩部格里芬直升機和一部[[C-130運輸機|C-130運輸機]]來進行搜救任務<ref>{{cite news

 | title      = Airlift Begins for Motorists Stranded on Hwy. 402 in Lambton County
 | first1     = Donald
 | last1      = McArthur
 | first2     = Dylan
 | last2      = Kristy
 | work       = The Star
 | location   = Windsor
 | date       = December 14, 2010}}</ref>。該段公路於同月16日早上重開<ref>{{cite news

 | title      = Canadian Highway Reopens After Snow Closure
 | first      = Matt
 | last       = Helms
 | work       = Detroit Free Press
 | location   = Michigan
 | date       = December 16, 2010}}</ref>。

有見402號公路西行前往藍水大橋的過境貨櫃車流量日增，省政府從2009年8月起在薩尼亞市内擴建402號公路，西行線從兩條增至四條，當中一條為[[NEXUS卡|NEXUS卡]]持卡人專線。工程於2012年8月完成<ref>{{cite news
 |title      = Highway 402 on track
 |first      = Dale
 |last       = Carruthers
 |publisher  = Sun Media
 |work       = The Observer
 |location   = Sarnia
 |date       = June 10, 2010
 |url        = http://www.theobserver.ca/ArticleDisplay.aspx?e=2624161
 |accessdate = June 24, 2010
}}{{Dead link|date=2018年9月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

